Welcome to our channel! Sophie and Zoey are two sisters who love to review EVERYTHING!! They love trying new things and sharing their views with the camera. We’ll be reviewing toys, movies, games, restaurants, candies, stores and more. 

Thank you so much for watching and we hope you subscribe and become a member of our family.
